## Fix result artifact contract

You MUST submit a `fix_result` artifact before declaring completion.
The complete grammar lives in `.agent/artifact-formats/fix_result.md`.

Submit one native-markdown document:

1. Use `type: fix_result` frontmatter, then `## Summary` (exactly one item:
   what you fixed and the evidence), `## Files Changed` (one item per file),
   and optionally `## Next Steps` (one item).
2. Submit with ralph_submit_md_artifact (`artifact_type="fix_result"`,
   `content` = the full markdown document — never JSON).
3. If the submit tool is unavailable, write the same complete document to
   `.agent/tmp/fix_result.md` instead.

